    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Email Remarketing\nMain campaign flow + 3 secondary cron chains (analytics, suppression sweep, queue flush) — same file, separate triggers (split into own workflows in prod per plan.md).\n\nDISABLED nodes:\n- **Send via platform** → OQ-1 (HubSpot Marketing Hub vs Mailchimp).\n- **Notify Guillermo / 48h summary** → OQ-G7 (alert channel).\n- **Get platform analytics** → OQ-1 (depends on chosen platform).\n\nDry-run gate is ON by default: first send of every campaign must run as mode=dry-run (lists recipients, no send). Idempotency = (campaign_id, contact_id), no TTL.",
        "height": 360,
        "width": 440,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "sticky-doc",
      "name": "Build notes",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-100, 20]
    },
